conversation.content: What should I do today? It's Friday and I've already done Push on Monday, Pull on Wednesday, and Legs on Thursday this week.
Great job staying consistent this week! Based on your training split, I'd recommend doing a Push workout today. Focus on compound movements like bench press and overhead press.
But I already did Push on Monday. Shouldn't I do Upper or Lower instead since I've done Push/Pull/Legs already?

You're absolutely right! I apologize for the confusion. Since you've completed Push, Pull, and Legs this week, an Upper body workout would be perfect for today. This will give you a full-body split for the week.
